summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Worth Fiftieth Street from Phinney Avenue to First Avenue Northwest et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing watermains & under Ordinance No. 26742, creating Local Improvement District No. 2467 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
